<h2 class="heading">Are you sure you want to do this?</h2>

<p>Releasing a Hard Drive cannot be undone.</p>

<p>
  Once executed, the Hard Drive will be detached from all Virtual
  Machines, and those <strong>machines will stop functioning</strong>.
</p>

<p>Are you sure you want to do this?</p>

<%= form_tag(hd_release_path, :method => :delete) do %>
  <%= submit_tag "Yes, I'm sure." %>
<% end %>
